==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sea pass
<hw>Sea" pass`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A document carried by neutral
merchant vessels in time of war, to show their nationality; a sea letter
or passport. See <er>Passport</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sea peach</ent>⟦br⟧
